<span id="freeTextContainer12010327777062151795">William Hanna wrote so many interesting theories about the issues of the world today. These issues are about Mynmar and the Rohingya tribe; President Trump&apos;s character and leadership; human trafficking in Israel; deaths caused by malaria and AIDS; the West’s generosity in providing aid and loans to developing countries which seems to be a smokescreen to the continued plunder of the natural resources of developing nations; the meaning of DEMOCRACY and so many more! Among those which I highly reso</span>
  <span id="freeText12010327777062151795" style="display:none">William Hanna wrote so many interesting theories about the issues of the world today. These issues are about Mynmar and the Rohingya tribe; President Trump's character and leadership; human trafficking in Israel; deaths caused by malaria and AIDS; the West’s generosity in providing aid and loans to developing countries which seems to be a smokescreen to the continued plunder of the natural resources of developing nations; the meaning of DEMOCRACY and so many more! Among those which I highly resonated with is about Democracy. He had pointed out that: <br /><br />"Any potential for genuine democracy in the West has been obliterated with governments being selected by the few rather than elected by the majority; with the people no longer— either ideologically or philosophically — challenging or debating the manner in which civilization on this planet is evolving; with an efficiently orchestrated and choreographed brainwashing that prevents people from thinking for themselves about the issues currently afflicting most of humanity; and with mainstream media complicity in democracy’s suppression. <br /><br />Corporate media today is a fully international and highly concentrated entity primarily concerned with the promotion of product sales and procapitalistic propaganda through the psychological control of human desires, emotions, beliefs, fears, and values".<br /><br />We have been brainwashed, and we had allowed this to go on for a long time! It's sad, and yet it's also something that gives us hope because being fed with this information is a chance to wake up and finally do the right thing! <br /></span>
  <a data-text-id="12010327777062151795" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

